95S.F.summary: Insr Insurance Group ASA, a non-life insurance company, focuses on property and casualty insurance for the retail, and small and medium sized enterprises in Norway. It serves customers through insurance agents and partners. The company was formerly known as Vardia Insurance Group ASA and changed its name to Insr Insurance Group ASA in October 2016. Insr Insurance Group ASA was founded in 2009 and is headquartered in Oslo, Norway.
